      • getTimestampFramePosition

        public long getTimestampFramePosition()
        Description copied from class: DefaultAudioSink.AudioTrackUtil
        Returns the AudioTimestamp.framePosition obtained during the most recent call to DefaultAudioSink.AudioTrackUtil.updateTimestamp() that returned true. The value is adjusted so that wrap around only occurs if the value exceeds Long.MAX_VALUE (which in practice will never happen).
